Enjoy trying these old-fashioned cake icing recipes. It is always nice to have a good cake frosting recipe handy when you wish to decorate a cake for a special occasion or to simply have it look special.<br><br>Would you like more vintage frosting recipes? Be sure to see...<br><br>
